A video of a knife-wielding man defending himself is doing the rounds on social media. The man is seen warding off three people approaching his vehicle. #dstv403 JOHANNESBURG - A video of a knife-wielding man defending himself is doing the rounds on social media. The incident reportedly took place in Klerksdorp in the North West Province. The man is seen warding off three people approaching his vehicle. They disperse after he threatens and shouts at them. He then gets into his vehicle after the confrontation. * eNCA is trying to get comment from the Klerksdorp police and will update you on developments.